<br>
My guild does Cursed and Seru regularly, we've just killed Emp twice and are preparing for VT in the next few weeks most likely. We're also flagged for Tactics but may not get to the Twins for a little while given our VT focus.<br>
<br>
There are only 4 immediately available neck items I saw worth it that I'm likely to see soonish: Seru's Torque (mega resists), Opaline Charm (goes cheap DKP wise), Pendant of Malosini, or the Mana Pres4 neck from one of the Twins.<br>
<br>
Keeping in mind with Seru / Opaline I can swap them down to lower slots than my neck later on what would you guys go for, or is there another nearby VT/non-elemental neck that you'd suggest ? I was thinking go for Torque or Opaline and then sit tight until I got points up again for one of the Pendant or Mana4 necks then swap the Torque down to my wrist. Opinions ?<br>
<br>
