There are much better mana preservation items in VT then the neck from the twins.<br>
<br>
Waiting for seru's torque is great, but his spawn time sucks and he has never dropped the torque in the multiple times we have killed him.<br>
<br>
I would go with a gloves, arms, belt upgrade first and get the 65/65 neck.<br>
